com.facebook.buck.android

Class DummyRDotJava

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.AbstractBuildable
      • com.facebook.buck.android.DummyRDotJava
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasJavaAbi, HasBuildTarget, AbiRule, Buildable, InitializableFromDisk<DummyRDotJava.BuildOutput>

    public class DummyRDotJava
extends AbstractBuildable
implements AbiRule, HasJavaAbi, InitializableFromDisk<DummyRDotJava.BuildOutput>
    Buildable that takes in a list of HasAndroidResourceDeps and for each of these rules, first creates an R.java file using MergeAndroidResourcesStep and compiles it to generate a corresponding R.class file. These are called "dummy" R.java files since these are later merged together into a single R.java file by AaptStep.

      • getAbiKey

        public Sha1HashCode getAbiKey()
        Description copied from interface: HasJavaAbi
        Returns a SHA-1 hash that represents the ABI for the Java files that are compiled by this rule. The only requirement on the hash is that equal hashes imply equal ABIs.

        Because the ABI is computed as part of the build process, this rule cannot be invoked until after this rule is built.
